      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you, it's a dream to drive! It\u2019s been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Honestly, it's in pristine shape\u2014no scratches, no smells, just pure perfection. I've taken such good care of it, and I know you're going to love it as much as I have. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
